title: SVENGOOLIE - Inner Sanctum: The Frozen Ghost-(1945) 9/3/2016 Cha
description:
Original broadcast date : 9/3/2016 with new mail segment from the rebroadcast on 12/3/2017
This is the fourth film in the Inner Sanctum series, all starring Lon Chaney Jr.


Plot :
A stage mentalist (Chaney)  involved in a mysterious death and a discredited plastic surgeon ( Koslek ) are among the assorted characters involved in mysterious goings-on in an eerie wax museum....

Cast::

Lon Chaney, Jr.
Evelyn Ankers
Martin Koslek 
Elena Verdugo

At the end, this has new segments from the 12/3/2017 Re-broadcast featuring a Little Caesars commercial, and a different mail segment including a SCENE Revision of Freddie "Boom Boom" Cannon's song, "The Svengoolie Stomp" , not featured in the original broadcast.
(I Apologize, I made an error in the screen text introduction and unable to correct it.)

I used a dvd print of the movie for a better Film presentation, while maintaining the original broadcast as close as possible . I hope you enjoy.
Requests welcome.
whodude33
